            <h1>Return Policy</h1>
            <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 10/07/2023</p>
            <p>At Grocefy Online, we are committed to your satisfaction and strive to provide you with the freshest and highest-quality products. If, for any reason, you are not completely satisfied with your purchase, please review our return policy below.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>1. Eligibility for Returns</h2>
            <p>You may be eligible for a return or refund under the following conditions:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Damaged or Defective Products:</strong> If you receive products that are damaged, defective, or spoiled, please contact our customer support team within 7 days of delivery. We will work with you to resolve the issue promptly.</li>
                <li><strong>Incorrect Items:</strong> If you receive items that differ from what you ordered, please notify us within 3 days of delivery. We will arrange for the correct items to be sent to you, or you may request a refund or credit.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Add this section to your existing HTML -->
        <section>
            <h2>2. Non-Returnable Items</h2>
            <p>Due to the nature of our products, we are unable to accept returns for the following items:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Perishable goods:</strong> Perishable goods, such as fresh produce, dairy, and meat, are non-returnable, except in cases of damage or spoilage.</li>
                <li><strong>Expired Shelf Life:</strong> Items with an expired shelf life at the time of delivery are non-returnable.</li>
                <li><strong>Opened or Used Products:</strong> Products that have been opened, used, or partially consumed are non-returnable.</li>
                <li><strong>Bundled or Promotional Items:</strong> Items purchased as part of a bundle or promotion may need to be returned as a complete set.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>3. How to Initiate a Return</h2>
            <p>To initiate a return, please follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Contact our customer support team within the specified time frame, providing your order number and details of the issue.</li>
                <li>Our team will guide you through the return process, which may include providing photographs of damaged or incorrect items for verification purposes.</li>
                <li>Depending on the circumstances, we will arrange for a replacement, refund, or credit to your Grocefy Online account.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>4. Refunds and Credits</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> Refunds for eligible returns will be processed using the original payment method within [number] business days of approval. Please note that it may take additional time for the refund to reflect in your account, depending on your financial institution.</li>
                <li><strong>Credits:</strong> Credits for Grocefy Online accounts will be issued promptly and can be used towards future purchases.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>5. Return Shipping</h2>
            <p>In most cases, we will arrange for the pickup of the returned items at no additional cost to you. Please follow the instructions provided by our customer support team for returning the items.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance with a return, please contact our customer support team at grocefyonline@gmail.com.</p>
        </section>


        <section>
            <h2>7. Updates to this Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update our return policy from time to time to better serve our customers. Any changes to this policy will be reflected on our website and will be effective as of the effective date stated at the beginning of the policy.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <p>By shopping with Grocefy Online, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agreed to our return policy. We are here to ensure your shopping experience is as convenient and enjoyable as possible, and we appreciate your trust in us.</p>
